Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------OP------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.02,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}Escape
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:09.11,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}讓這風兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:11.86,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}帶走淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:15.74,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}不斷加速直到它乾涸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:19.95,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}翻越前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:22.46,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}那份答案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:29.30,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,445)\be2}一定在遙遠的天空彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:37.43,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}於不存在答案的此地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:42.10,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}深深歎息 仰望天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:48.15,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}染成深青色的瞳孔深處 閃耀著的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:50.94,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}是敢闖 敢夢想的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:53.03,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:55.03,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}Escape
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:57.07,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}讓這風兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:00:59.87,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}帶著心願
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:03.96,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}伸出手描繪未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:07.75,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}不再畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:10.46,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}淚水痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:15.76,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}染滿彩虹七色 徑直飛去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.44,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,445)\be2}那片天空的彼岸
